Dimensional reduction and clustering (latent space)¶

In [9]:
# Find clusters, then run UMAP, and visualize
so <- FindNeighbors(so, dims=1:30, reduction="latent", assay="SCVI_dim30", graph.name=c("SCVI_nn", "SCVI_snn"), return.neighbor=FALSE, verbose=FALSE)
so <- FindClusters(so, algorithm=4, graph.name="SCVI_snn", random.seed=random_seed, verbose=FALSE)
so <- RunUMAP(so, dims=1:30, reduction="latent", umap.method="umap-learn", seed.use=random_seed, verbose=FALSE)
In [10]:
options(repr.plot.width=15, repr.plot.height=10)
dplot_1(so, cluster="seurat_clusters")
In [11]:
